{"tid":2516755,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟將立法 防堵中資併購和參與招標","createTime":"2021-05-05T00:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T11:20:13.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c18467034f88cf79004ef7a98aa8e85a078cbd74","tid":2516755,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:42:35.000Z","msg":"歐盟將立法 防堵中資併購和參與招標<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5434336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F5434336&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKwZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=4294fd0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5434336</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟即將提出新法，防堵中資併購歐洲企業和參與招標，反制中國的國家資本主義，未來這部法案將與各國審查外資併購的機制相輔相成。<br />\n<br />\n「南德日報」（S&uuml;ddeutsche Zeitung）報導，歐盟執委會5日將建議立法，阻止獲政府補貼的外國企業併購歐盟企業、或參與歐盟的公開招標。<strong><span class=\"red\">儘管條文沒有直接點名中國，只在註腳和說明提到中國，不過顯然是針對中資企業而來。</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n近年來，愈來愈多歐盟國家擔心中資企業在官方主導下，利用政府提供的優厚補貼併購歐洲的尖端科技和打擊歐洲的競爭者，最著名的例子是中國家電大廠美的集團2016年併購德國機器人大廠庫卡（Kuka）引發的技術外流疑慮。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n根據該報取得的規章草案，歐盟執委會在立法理由指出，外國企業獲政府補貼併購歐盟企業或破壞公平競爭的例子愈來愈多，有扭曲市場的風險，德國反壟斷委員會（The Monopolies Commission）去年7月發布的一份報告也要求歐洲制定嚴格規範，反制中國的「國家資本主義」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">歐盟的27個會員國當中，目前有18國透過國內法限制外資併購能源、高科技等產業，歐盟這部新法針對的是外國政府的補貼，將與各國的審查機制相輔相成。<br />\n<br />\n不過，按照歐盟立法程序，執委會提出法案後，還需經歐洲議會和部長會議批准，幾年後才會實施。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n歐盟近來為強調自主性，站出來捍衛自身利益的動作愈來愈大。主管競爭的歐盟執委維斯塔哲（Margrethe Vestager）推動此案的時間點，歐盟與中國的關係正好出現惡化跡象，雙方由於新疆維吾爾少數民族受迫害問題互相制裁。"},{"pid":"7f9af360e9d0621f390ffd43cb20d81e8da6c737","tid":2516755,"uid":243677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:43:27.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35c81f63c642f7564f352b5731e96b67f2d69ce","tid":2516755,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/09/maxresdefault-4-22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fmaxresdefault-4-22.jpg&h=36b71f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/08/600x400-GettyImages-866170226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F600x400-GettyImages-866170226.jpg&h=a7ff290b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"190fa38dbefcf89821032e3e61a38f535f2b986e","tid":2516755,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:44:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecca7dd807b0907b2e1b6c4d5c99f121cd4e3d09","tid":2516755,"uid":238117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:47:07.000Z","msg":"一日最衰刁總<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬: <span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>點解要攬炒</strong></span>"},{"pid":"945bdc06822fd809619ed1647e0193c020ada03a","tid":2516755,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}